      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DRAGON SCROLL (3) well-related filly resuming. Comes up from Victoria after struggling on debut in the soft (7) going when seventh over 1017m at Moe last September. Primed for this with the two sound trials and the in-form Rachel King hops aboard. Go close. SAMMY THE BULL (6) fitter with racing and doesn't have to improve much to shed his Maiden tag. Closed strongly at the big odds when third over this track and trip. Can sit off the fast speed and take a hand in the finish. REDZERO (5) bumped into a smart type first-up with a narrow on-pace second over 1000m at Scone. Back in good order and capable of taking this out. STELLAA LASS (7) covered a stack of ground on debut with a plugging second over 1000m at Wyong in a Super Mdn. Fitter now from the low draw and look for a better performance.",
